# SSH configuration

Host *
    AddKeysToAgent yes
    UseKeychain yes
    ServerAliveInterval 60
    ServerAliveCountMax 10
    TCPKeepAlive yes
    
# GitHub
Host github.com
    HostName github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa
    
